The Following Packages We Need To Build This Program
==================================
sqlite3
libsqlite3-dev
==================================

Try To Use Following Commands to Install[As Root]
==================================
apt-get install sqlite3 libsqlite3-dev   --->> For Debian,Ubuntu,Anthon And Other OS which use DPKG Package Manager
yum install sqlite3 libsqlite3-dev       --->> For Red Hat,OpenSuse,Arch And Other OS Which use RPM Package Manager
==================================
